last_episode_to_air.name: A House Divided
last_episode_to_air.overview: An unexpected visitor hatches a plan that could destroy humankind unless Mulligan can act fast. But all of his cabinet — except Lucy — has abandoned him.

name: Mulligan
overview: In this satirical comedy, when most of Earth is destroyed by aliens, can a few survivors rebuild what’s left of America and form a more perfect union?

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: A regular guy named Mulligan is made President after helping stop an alien invasion of Earth.

episodes.name: The Great Mulligan
episodes.overview: After blowing up an alien army and saving humanity from extinction, regular guy Mulligan must figure out how to lead his fellow survivors as president.

episodes.name: Morning in America
episodes.overview: To start rebuilding society, Simon and Farrah ask Mulligan if they can take a census. But there's one thing they didn't count on: catching feelings.

episodes.name: Grand Old Party
episodes.overview: With only 1,132 people left on Earth, Mulligan throws an epic party at the White House in hopes to out-rage former presidents — and make Lucy jealous.

episodes.name: The Stamp Act
episodes.overview: Women outnumber men two to one! To distract the fairer sex from their obvious advantage, Senator LaMarr proposes a contest to feature a woman on a stamp.

episodes.name: The Stench
episodes.overview: First Lady Lucy takes up her latest cause: a benefit concert called "Quench the Stench" to eradicate a pervasive and putrid odor plaguing D.C.

episodes.name: Opening Day
episodes.overview: If Simon and Lucy want Mulligan to sign an executive order for solar power, they'll have to go through the proper protocol: seducing Senator LaMarr.

episodes.name: The Egg Hunt
episodes.overview: On Easter, Senator LaMarr worries traditional religion may be losing its influence on their new government until he meets a doomsday prophet named Dave.

episodes.name: Matty's Treasure: Book of Seeds
episodes.overview: To get Mulligan on board to raid the seed vault in Maryland, Simon and Farrah tell him they're on a quest for the legendary national treasure.

episodes.name: Not My President
episodes.overview: If former President Brad Chadman survived the invasion in an alien-proof bunker, will Mulligan take one for the team and relinquish his power?

episodes.name: The Love Choice
episodes.overview: In an effort to display more transparency in government, the Cabinet decides to hold a public election, which quickly devolves into a reality show.

episodes.name: A Rising Tide
episodes.overview: Mulligan tries to convince cruise ship passengers — and potential future voters — to join him on land, but the Thirsty Princess is just too much fun.

episodes.name: Party Foul
episodes.overview: Aboard the cruise ship, Lucy and Zhao suspect the Fun Police are up to no good. Back on land, Mulligan turns America over to the United Kingdom.

episodes.name: The Great Depression
episodes.overview: While Farrah searches for TOD in an abandoned shopping mall, the rest of the cabinet suffers from post-boat blues — except for a repressed Mulligan.

episodes.name: Sic Semper Mulligan
episodes.overview: When Mulligan learns about presidential assassinations, he changes his policies to avoid a similar fate. Meanwhile, Farrah worries she's mothering TOD.

episodes.name: DC/AC
episodes.overview: During a heatwave, Farrah tries to prevent a power outage, Mulligan keeps the only copy of the Constitution safe, and LaMarr spends time with family.

episodes.name: The Ballad of Sentient Meat
episodes.overview: When food becomes scarce, Mulligan and Lucy go on a campaign to promote vegetables while Farrah tries to create an ethical alternative to meat in a lab.

episodes.name: Watergate Watergate
episodes.overview: The Mulligan administration announces a lottery for free housing, but there's one catch: no running water. Can the only plumber left on Earth help?

episodes.name: Dr. Johnny's Wonder Pill
episodes.overview: When Zhao asks LaMarr for help fast-tracking a wonder drug, LaMarr knows just the president who can get it approved... in exchange for a shiny trophy.

episodes.name: Camp David
episodes.overview: The cabinet heads to Camp David to solve issues with the UK in a good old fashioned peace summit — if they can survive homesickness and camp crushes.

episodes.name: A House Divided
episodes.overview: An unexpected visitor hatches a plan that could destroy humankind unless Mulligan can act fast. But all of his cabinet — except Lucy — has abandoned him.
